    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine is very tender, scoop the <strong>softened flesh</strong> out of the skins with a fork, discard the skins</p><p>Tip: Carefully hold the stalks (they will be hot!) to scrape the flesh out easily</p><p>Chop the <strong>scooped aubergine flesh</strong> finely</p>",
